dct_title_s: S. R. I. Sueviæ circulus atq. ducatus
dct_alternative_sm: Sacri romani imperii Sueviæ circulus atque ducatus
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially, and by shading.
Bar scale on map, given in "Milliaria Germanica communia" (also "Gemeene Duytsche Mylen").
Appears in Visscher's Atlas minor: sive totius orbus terrarum, 1698.
